# Agent harness session state + nested worktrees (not part of this repo's lint/test scope).
# Ignored as a whole directory, not `.claude/*`: grok's file watcher only tests the repo's
# immediate children against .gitignore, then watches each survivor recursively. `.claude/*`
# leaves `.claude` itself unignored, so grok walked into .claude/worktrees and took ~150K
# inotify watches per session (issue #226). `.claude/settings.json` stays tracked because
# ignore rules never apply to files already in the index; adding new ones needs `git add -f`.
.claude/
.claire/
.worktrees/
test-results/

# bun build --compile artifacts
dist-bun/

# Headless self-update DEV signing key (private half; pubkey is committed). Never commit.
scripts/.podium-update-dev.key
# Headless update artifacts produced by build-bun.ts
podium-headless-*.tar.gz
podium-headless-*.tar.gz.sig

# Local profiling/diagnostic clutter
report.*.json
mon.pid

# Agent-local test tempdirs (never commit)
.tmp-claude/
